        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued October 15 at 7:18AM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 718 AM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Costilla, or 22 miles north of Questa, moving northeast at 50 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 40 mph and half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
San Luis, San Pablo, Cuchara, Sanchez Reservoir, Chama, and Garcia.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
